{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回 伯仲双侠\n\n萧十一郎在牡丹楼为冰冰强买柳苏州的耳环，出价一万六两银子迫使柳苏州让出座位。冰冰却说不喜欢耳环，萧十一郎随手将其抛出窗外。风四娘与沈璧君在旁目睹，风四娘对萧十一郎的变化痛心不已。\n\n冰冰故意挑衅\"伯仲双侠\"欧阳兄弟，称讨厌他们的眼睛。萧十一郎会意，逼迫欧阳兄弟自挖双眼。欧阳文仲不服，萧十一郎提出三招之约：若兄弟俩能接住三招便作罢，否则自挖双眼。欧阳兄弟使子母离魂圈和镔铁鸳鸯拐应战，但萧十一郎仅用三招便将二人击倒——第一招虚晃吸引注意，第二招逼二人近身，第三招夺圈伤人。冰冰逼迫兄弟兑现承诺，欧阳兄弟正要互挖眼珠时，突然有人大声阻止。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "高刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你就是萧十一郎？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "高刚",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "他说他喜欢留在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_gao_gang",
      "text": "我听见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "高刚",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "他就是萧十一郎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_gao_gang",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "高刚",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "萧十一郎若说他喜欢留在这里，就没有人能要他走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_gao_gang",
      "text": "他不走，你走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_gang",
      "speaker_name": "高刚",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "好，我走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我实在不知道你就是萧十一郎。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "现在你已知道了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你真的喜欢这副耳环？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "不是我喜欢，是她喜欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "她喜欢的东西，你都给她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "她喜欢的东西，我都给她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "好，那么我就送给你，我们交个朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "我不要你送，也不想交你这种朋友。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你想怎么样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "这副耳环也是你买下来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "用多少银子买的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "八千两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "我给你一万六千两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shu_tong",
      "speaker_name": "书僮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是杨家的'源记'票号开出来的银票，十足兑现。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "给他。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在耳环已是你的了，若没有什么别的事，阁下不妨请便。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "我还有样别的事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "还有什么事？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "我说过，我喜欢这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你……你难道要我把这位子让给你？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "柳苏州",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我……我若不肯让呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_su_zhou",
      "text": "你一定会让的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "这耳环的颜色果然很好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "现在你已不喜欢它了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "它让你惹了这么多麻烦，我怎么还会喜欢它？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你既然已不喜欢它，我看着它也讨厌了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "这位姑娘是在跟我们说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我们和姑娘素不相识，姑娘有什么指教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "你们不认得我，我却认得你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "哦……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "你叫欧阳文仲，他叫欧阳文伯，兄弟两个人都不是好东西。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文伯",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我兄弟难道还有什么地方得罪了姑娘？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "你们自己不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你也不认得他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但他们却老是用眼睛瞪着我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我不喜欢别人用眼睛瞪着我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我也不喜欢他们的眼睛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你不喜欢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我简直讨厌极了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "两位听见她说的话没有？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "她说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "她说她不喜欢你们的眼睛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "眼睛长在我们自己身上，本就用不着别人喜欢。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "别人既然讨厌你们的眼睛，你们还要这双眼睛干什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文伯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "我的意思你应明白的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你难道要我们挖出这双眼睛来？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "的确有这意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "既然如此，你为什么不过来动手？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "眼睛是你们自己的，为什么要我去动手？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个人居然要我们自己挖出自己的眼睛来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "自己挖出眼睛，至少总比被人砍下脑袋好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "镔铁鸳鸯拐，和子母离魂圈？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "自从昔年十二连环坞的要命金老七去世后，江湖中好像就没有人再用'子母离魂圈'这种兵刃了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "据说这种兵刃的招式变化最奇特，和所有的软硬兵刃都完全不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "因为这种兵刃既不长，也不短，既不软，也不硬，若没有十五年以上的火候，就很难施展。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "所以江湖中用这种兵刃的人一向不多，能用这种兵刃的，就一定是高手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "看来你的见识果然不差。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "镔铁鸳鸯拐，一长一短，也是种很难练的外门兵器，而且其中还可以夹带着暗器，据说昔年的太湖三杰，就是死在这双兵器下的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "死在这只铁拐下的人，又何止太湖三杰而已！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "两位出身名门，用的也是这种极少见的外门兵器，武功想必是不错的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "倒还过得去。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "现在你们不妨一齐出手，只要你们能接得住我三招，我就……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你就怎么样？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "我就自己挖出自己这双眼珠子来，送给你们。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好气概，好一个萧十一郎。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧十一郎无论是好是坏，说出来的话，倒从来没有不算数的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文伯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我兄弟若连你三招都接不住，以后也无颜见人了，倒不如索性挖出这双眼睛来，倒落得个干净。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "既然如此，你们还等什么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你只要我们接你三招？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "不错，三招……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！好兵器。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "用这种兵刃杀人，看来实在容易得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文伯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "的确不难。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "你们今日若能挡得住我三招，不但立刻名扬天下，而且名利双收，看来好像也并不困难。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "只可惜天下绝没有这种便宜的事，我既然敢答应你们，就当然有把握。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文伯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你若是想用这种话来扰乱我们的情绪，你就打错主意了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我兄弟身经大小数百战，还没有一个人单凭几句话就将我们吓倒。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "我只不过想提醒你们一件事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文伯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "我只希望你们莫要忘了我用的是什么刀。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "割鹿刀？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "不错，割鹿刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "你们总该知道，这是柄削铁如泥的宝刀，连六十三斤重的镔铁鸳鸯拐，也一样能削得断的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "text": "所以我劝你们，最好莫要用兵器来架我的刀。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是第一招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你好像只用一招，就已将他们击倒了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我用了三招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你那第一招也有用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "当然有用，每一招都有用。第一招是为了要吸引他们的注意力，让他们全副精神都集中在这柄刀上，他们的身法也自然会慢了下来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "第二招呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "第二招是为了要将他们两个人逼在一起，也为的是要他不来防备我的左手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "第三招就是真正致命的一招了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "他们现在还活着，只因为我并不想要他们的命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "看来不但你这三招都有用，连你说的那些话，也都有用的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "但说话是吓不倒人的，也不能算伤人的招式。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "所以你还是只用了三招？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我只用了三招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "所以他们已输了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "我兄弟若连你三招都接不住，以后也无颜见人了，倒不如索性挖出这双眼睛来，也落得个干净。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "你还记得这句话是谁说的？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "现在你们是不是已输了？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "既然输了，你们现在还等什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文伯",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我兄弟虽然学艺不精，却也不是言而无信的人。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "很好，我也希望你们不是言而无信的人，因为你们赖也赖不掉的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_wen_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳文仲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_wen_bo",
      "text": "你挖我的，我挖你的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
